          <h1 class="f2 fw6 f1-ns lh-1_1 measure mt0 sky">
            Automated data availability and <br/>
            redundancy on IPFS
          </h1>
          <h2 class="f4 f3-ns fw4 lh-1_3 b measure dib-m arctic-teal">
            IPFS Cluster provides data orchestration across a swarm of IPFS daemons by allocating, replicating and tracking a global pinset distributed among multiple peers.
          </h2>
          <p>
            <a class="github-button" href="https://github.com/ipfs-cluster/ipfs-cluster" data-icon="octicon-star" data-size="large" data-show-count="true" aria-label="Star ipfs-cluster/ipfs-cluster on GitHub">Star</a>
            <a class="github-button" href="https://github.com/ipfs-cluster/ipfs-cluster/subscription" data-icon="octicon-eye" data-size="large" aria-label="Watch ipfs-cluster/ipfs-cluster on GitHub">Watch</a>
            <a class="github-button" href="https://github.com/ipfs-cluster/ipfs-cluster/issues" data-icon="octicon-issue-opened" data-size="large" aria-label="Issue ipfs-cluster/ipfs-cluster on GitHub">Issues</a>
          </p>
